{"tid":346482,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"公告：種田梨沙回歸","createTime":"2017-08-04T03:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T02:26:47.000Z","uid":7307,"like":51,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"404fdedb866956caec2d9e41e4201ff5d75c864c","tid":346482,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:53:03.000Z","msg":"拝啓<br />\n <br />\n平素は格別のご高配を賜り、厚く御礼申し上げます。<br />\n <br />\n弊社所属俳優の種田梨沙ですが、<br />\nかねてより喉の治療の為お休みさせて頂いておりましたが、<br />\nこの度体調を考慮しながらではありますが、少しずつお仕事を再開させて頂く予定です。<br />\nファンの皆様、関係者の皆様におかれましては、<br />\n多大なるご心配とご迷惑をお掛け致しました事を心よりお詫び申し上げます。<br />\n <br />\n今後とも変わらぬご声援、ご支援賜りますよう宜しくお願い申し上げます。<br />\n <br />\n　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　敬具<br />\n　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　株式会社 大沢事務所<br />\n<br />\n總之做返野"},{"pid":"ab519e83912188e071a8724cfd5bc6e6ffc8ebc5","tid":346482,"uid":55262,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b2294f30cae2d1c83fd0f6535f7ee79733bd49","tid":346482,"uid":45373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abbff4398d6e111d8c06c3754a807003fedb07b","tid":346482,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:57:10.000Z","msg":"休左幾多個月？"},{"pid":"5aa5143a5d77b02ce177d6043d9620b72ef5cf58","tid":346482,"uid":10197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\